<p align="CENTER"><font size="6" color="Green" face="Brush Script MT"><img border="0" src="/web/20001013113215im_/http://www.jericho-city.org/Corel/Crstlbal.gif" width="20" height="20">Jericho Municipality News<font size="6" color="Green" face="Brush Script MT"><img border="0" src="/web/20001013113215im_/http://www.jericho-city.org/Corel/Crstlbal.gif" width="20" height="20"></font></font>
